# Code Skill: Video

Load this rule for the implementation guidance for video or multimedia slides.

## Required patterns

- Use a thumbnail `Image()` when one is available. Otherwise use a dark `Rect` as the player backdrop.
- Simulate the player UI with a play button overlay.
- Simulate a progress bar with a track and a foreground progress element.
- Bundle the player pieces into one `Group` before adding it to the frame.

## Layout guidance

- Keep the video area dominant and close to 16:9.
- Center the play button with explicit math or parent alignment instead of relying on implicit placement.
